# To-Do App

A simple To-Do application built to manage tasks efficiently. This app allows users to create, edit, mark as complete, and delete tasks.

## Features

- **Add a task:** Users can add a new task.
- **Edit a task:** Users can update an existing task.
- **Complete a task:** Users can mark a task as complete.
- **Delete a task:** Users can remove a task from the list.
- **Responsive design:** The app is fully responsive and works on mobile, tablet, and desktop devices.

## Technologies Used

- **HTML**
- **CSS**
- **JavaScript**
- **LocalStorage** (for storing tasks on the client side)
